 person susceptible to other life threatening infections or conditions, or as may be defined by the Sindh AIDS Commission from time to time; Preamble. Short title, extent and commencement. Definitions.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "94565634-c8fd-4247-bbf0-851f39ec4534": {"__data__": {"id_": "94565634-c8fd-4247-bbf0-851f39ec4534", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/scan-law-and-policies-affecting-human-rights-discrimination-and-access-hiv-and-health-services-key-populations-pakistan", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Scan of Law and Policies Affecting Human Rights, Discrimination and Access to HIV and Health Services by Key Populations in Pakistan", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/scan-law-and-policies-affecting-human-rights-discrimination-and-access-hiv-and-health-services-key-populations-pakistan", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "813988933f5e3e2d3bf79344d26efba9a8ab7924924c27f14c178d5484f60c74"}, "2": {"node_id": "f0da47d8-d20f-4178-a575-f4ba62aa4959", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/scan-law-and-policies-affecting-human-rights-discrimination-and-access-hiv-and-health-services-key-populations-pakistan", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "6e4e38f4507cc7678dcc453fdf45287dfe511e17641ee6d5285ce0f8280da083"}}, "hash": "33820b85c6fdbdeb12bc03654f30efc3bdcfc1d31f